<rml>
<head>
  <link type="text/rcss" href="showcase.rcss"/>
  <!-- EN: CI/headless version of the showcase — identical to showcase.rml except the mask card
           is omitted because Mesa llvmpipe's software rasterizer crashes on the BlendMask
           dual-sampler shader (free(): invalid next size). This is a Mesa SW renderer bug,
           not a glintfx bug. Use showcase.rml for the full demo on real GPU hardware.
       PT: Versão CI/headless do showcase — idêntica ao showcase.rml exceto pelo card mask,
           omitido porque o rasterizador de software llvmpipe do Mesa crasha no shader BlendMask
           dual-sampler (free(): invalid next size). Bug do Mesa, não do glintfx.
           Use showcase.rml para o demo completo em GPU real. -->
  <title>glintfx showcase (CI/headless)</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="section-dark">
    <div class="card glow">Glow + shadow</div>
    <div class="card grad">Gradient</div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-gradient">
    <div class="card blur">Backdrop blur</div>
  </div>
</body>
</rml>
